manifests.contents:
bench = []
test = []
example = []

[[bin]]
path = "src/bin/daemon/main.rs"
name = "trade-hostd"
test = true
doctest = true
bench = true
doc = true
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
harness = true
required-features = []

[package]
name = "trade-host"
edition = "2021"
version = "0.0.1"
authors = []
keywords = []
categories = []
autobins = true
autoexamples = true
autotests = true
autobenches = true
publish = true

[dependencies]
async-trait = "0.1.53"
atty = "0.2"
chashmap = "2.2.2"
chrono = "0.4"
colored = "2.0.0"
crossbeam-channel = "0.5.4"
dotenv = "0.15.0"
envy = "0.4"
quinn = "0.8.2"
rcgen = "0.9.2"
rustls = "0.20.5"
rustls-pemfile = "1.0.0"
teloc = "0.2.0"
time = "0.3.9"
tracing = "0.1.34"
tracing-bunyan-formatter = "0.3.2"
tracing-core = "0.1.26"
tracing-opentelemetry = "0.17.2"
x509-parser = "0.13.2"

[dependencies.binance-rs-async]
version = "1.1.5"
features = ["rustls-tls", "all_apis"]
optional = false
default-features = false

[dependencies.futures-util]
version = "0.3.21"
features = []
optional = false

[dependencies.k8s-openapi]
version = "0.15.0"
features = ["v1_24"]
optional = false

[dependencies.kube]
version = "0.73.0"
features = ["runtime", "derive"]
optional = false

[dependencies.opentelemetry]
version = "0.17.0"
features = ["rt-tokio"]
optional = false

[dependencies.opentelemetry-jaeger]
version = "0.16.0"
features = ["rt-tokio", "collector_client", "isahc_collector_client"]
optional = false

[dependencies.serde]
version = "1.0.137"
features = ["derive"]
optional = false

[dependencies.tokio]
version = "1.18.1"
features = ["full"]
optional = false

[dependencies.tracing-futures]
version = "0.2.5"
features = []
optional = false

[dependencies.tracing-subscriber]
version = "0.3"
features = ["registry", "env-filter"]
optional = false

[dependencies.trade-core]
path = "../trade-core"
features = []
optional = false

[dependencies.trade-protocol]
path = "../trade-protocol"
features = []
optional = false

[lib]
path = "src/lib.rs"
name = "trade_host"
test = true
doctest = true
bench = true
doc = true
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
harness = true
edition = "2021"
required-features = []
crate-type = ["rlib"]
